-- Shanked Golf Shots Are Part of Game, New York Court Says in Injury Ruling
-- B y   D o n   J e f f r e y
-- 2010-12-21T15:06:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/shanked-golf-shots-are-part-of-game-new-york-court-says-in-injury-ruling.html
Shanked golf shots are part of the
assumed risks of the game, New York’s top state court ruled in
dismissing a lawsuit by a golfer blinded in one eye after being
struck by an errant ball hit by a player who didn’t yell “Fore!”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
